OL,3,CMoment police officer caught on camera
OL,4,Cstealing from Lidl supermarket
OL,6,FA police officer has been sentenced to
OL,7,Fan 18-month community order for
OL,8,Fshoplifting from a supermarket in
OL,9,FNorth Devon.
OL,11,FPolice Constable Christopher Spence,
OL,12,F44, was seen on CCTV placing a number
OL,13,Fof goods in his rucksack at a Lidl in
OL,14,FBideford but only paid for one item.
OL,16,FThe officer, who was off duty at the
OL,17,Ftime of the offence, is now subject to
OL,18,Fmisconduct proceedings within the
OL,19,Fforce. He has been suspended from duty
OL,20,Fsince his arrest.
