OL,3,CMoment police officer caught on camera
OL,4,Cstealing from Lidl supermarket
OL,6,FSpence had previously pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto a charge of theft from a shop on
OL,8,FMonday 12 February.
OL,10,FHe appeared before Exeter Crown Court
OL,11,Fon Tuesday 26 November for sentencing
OL,12,Fand was given an 18-month community
OL,13,Forder.
OL,15,FH was also told to do 150 hours unpaid
OL,16,Fwork, pay #300 towards prosecution
OL,17,Fcosts within 12 months, as well as a
OL,18,Fvictim surcharge and #30 compensation
OL,19,Fto the store.
