OL,3,CMoment police officer caught on camera
OL,4,Cstealing from Lidl supermarket
OL,6,FFollowing sentencing, Superintendent
OL,7,FToby Davies, Commander in North and
OL,8,FWest Devon, said: "We are deeply
OL,9,Fdisappointed by the actions of Chris
OL,10,FSpence, particularly given his
OL,11,Fneighbourhood role within the
OL,12,Fcommunity.
OL,14,F"First and foremost, I want to assure
OL,15,Four community that the action of one
OL,16,Findividual does not reflect the values
OL,17,For integrity of our local officers.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
