OL,6,F"We are committed to maintaining the
OL,7,Fhighest levels of trust and confidence
OL,8,Fin the community we serve, and I would
OL,9,Flike to assure the public that such
OL,10,Fincidents are rare.
OL,12,F"This behaviour undermines all those
OL,13,Fofficers who behave to the highest
OL,14,Fstandards day in, day out, keeping our
OL,15,Farea safe.
